title: Navigate forwards to a tab list in reading mode
instructions: Navigate to the tab list. Note: You may need to press certain commands (such as Down Arrow) multiple times to hear all information relating to the tab list.
assertions: roleTabList nameTabListEntertainment roleSelectedItemTab nameFocusedTabNilsFrahm stateFocusedTabSelected positionFocusedTab1 numberTabsTabList3

title: Navigate backwards to a tab list in reading mode
instructions: Navigate to the tab list. Note: You may need to press certain commands (such as Up Arrow) multiple times to hear all information relating to the tab list.
assertions: roleTabList nameTabListEntertainment roleSelectedItemTab nameFocusedTabJoke stateFocusedTabSelected positionFocusedTabTabList3 numberTabsTabList3

title: Request information about a tab in a tab list in reading mode
instructions: With the reading cursor on the 'Nils Frahm' tab, read information about the tab.

title: Navigate to the next tab in a tab list in reading mode
instructions: With the reading cursor on the 'Nils Frahm' tab, navigate to the next tab.

title: Navigate to the previous tab in a tab list in reading mode
instructions: With the reading cursor on the 'Agnes Obel' tab, navigate to the previous tab.

title: Navigate to the first tab in a tab list in interaction mode
instructions: With focus on the 'Joke' tab, navigate to the first tab.

title: Navigate to the last tab in a tab list in interaction mode
instructions: With focus on the 'Nils Frahm' tab, navigate to the last tab.

title: Navigate forwards to a tab panel in interaction mode
Navigate backwards to a tab panel in interaction mode
Activate a tab in a tab list in reading mode
instructions: With the reading cursor on the 'Agnes Obel' tab, activate the tab.

title: Delete a tab from a tab list in reading mode
instructions: With the reading cursor on the 'Joke' tab, delete the tab.
